### Register
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "john",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "password": "test1234",
    "password2": "test1234"
}

### Login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "john",
    "password": "test1234"
}

### Account Detail
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here

### Deposit
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/deposit/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here

{
    "amount": "1000.00",
    "description": "first deposit"
}

### Withdraw
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/withdraw/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here

{
    "amount": "500.00",
    "description": "ATM withdrawal"
}

### Transfer
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/transfer/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here

{
    "amount": "200.00",
    "target_account_number": "target-account-uuid-here",
    "description": "sending money"
}

### Transaction History
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/transactions/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here

### Transaction History filtered by type
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/account/transactions/?type=deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token your-token-here
